21:51.266 --> 21:52.049
The jury's still out.

21:53.964 --> 21:55.879
-Over there! Ha! No!

21:59.970 --> 22:02.886
-Hey.
-Hey.

22:03.017 --> 22:04.975
Still here then?

22:05.106 --> 22:06.107
Off tomorrow.

22:06.237 --> 22:08.805
Bon voyage, dosser.

22:08.936 --> 22:11.330
Yeah. Fair play.

22:21.905 --> 22:23.777
Gentlemen.

22:23.907 --> 22:25.169
My liberator.

22:25.300 --> 22:28.172
I never got a chance
to express my gratitude.

22:28.303 --> 22:30.218
Oh, don't thank me.

22:30.349 --> 22:32.002
It was all Mr. Wayne. Stopped
