in the end?

22:39.923 --> 22:40.968
Never you mind.

22:41.098 --> 22:42.665
Come.

22:42.796 --> 22:43.840
Join us.

22:43.971 --> 22:46.190
Just the one. I'm on duty.

22:46.321 --> 22:47.801
Alfred runs this place.

22:47.931 --> 22:49.368
My last night, I'm happy to say.

22:49.498 --> 22:51.761
Alfred and his mother
are on our same flight tomorrow.

22:53.023 --> 22:53.894
You're leaving, too?

22:54.024 --> 22:54.851
